author: Guerrilla Miniature Games
description:
It's more Full Spectrum Dominance, the Print-to-Play Sci Fi mass combat game with lovely models and rules all designed by The Lazy Forger. Having painted up my first army, I'm back with Bob to throw down a full sized 60-pt game using one of the three Pre-Built armies at 60pts for the Corsairs. Let's check it out!


STLS for models, terrain and the digital rules all available HERE: https://www.myminifactory.com/users/TheLazyForger?fbclid=IwY2xjawIIYK5leHRuA2FlbQIxMAABHeT0TiY_m-RwDp1UxT9QgbgvuwgdksRPLY50fQ75u98jUths1bVMvVo1KA_aem_n9MBH8OZymyIHxIvitCKsg#/

GMG is publicly supported. Become a backer on Patreon to ensure new content and that the Studio can continue: https://www.patreon.com/guerrillaminiaturegames
